<L>__{exterior skyscraper day}
<A>__{rocky steps off a bus in mid town philadelphia. he hurries down broad street. every few steps he breaks into a trot... he enters a skyscraper.}
<L>__{interior office building hall day}
<A>__{rocky exits the elevator and enters the office of miles jergens' productions.}
<L>__{interior jergens' productions day}
<A>__{the secretary is slightly startled by rocky's excited expression.}
<C>__{secretary}
<D>__{may i help you?}
<A>__{rocky hands her the business card.}
<C>__{secretary}
