<C>__{jergens}
<D>__{not spar, i'm asking whether you would be interested in fighting creed for the championship.}
<A>__{the weight of the statement comes crashing down in rocky. for a long moment he becomes nothing more than a basket case as he ponders the statement... he half regains his senses.}
